OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will have a dry, sunny
OL,6,Fand frosty start. Cloud will build
OL,7,Fthrough the morning with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers following in the afternoon,
OL,9,Fsome will be heavy and thundery with
OL,10,Fhail.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers, some heavy, will
OL,13,Fclear from the west during the
OL,14,Fevening. This will leave the night dry
OL,15,Fwith increasing clear spells, these
OL,16,Fleading to frost patches towards
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
