OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and a patchy frost.
OL,7,FCloud will spread northeast during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Outbreaks of rain, some
OL,9,Fheavy, spread northeast later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBands
OL,12,Fof rain push northeast with showers,
OL,13,Fsome heavy and thundery, following
OL,14,FWednesday. These showers continue
OL,15,FThursday morning. A further rain band
OL,16,Fpushes northeast Friday, showers
OL,17,Ffollow later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
